16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-1925.2A of Title 63, unless
18 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. The Oklahoma Health Care Authority in its annual budget
20 request submitted pursuant to Section 34.36 of Title 62 of the
21 Oklahoma Statutes shall include a supplemental item reflecting the
22 new state and federal funding necessary to meet the additional costs
23 associated with reimbursing nursing facilities and intermediate care
